Packages that use com.irurueta.algebra

Description
com.irurueta.algebra
This package contains classes related to algebra, such as Matrix class to contains matrices data and simple operations or Complex to handle computations with Complex numbers.
com.irurueta.statistics
This package contains classes related to statistics, but that also has dependencies onf algebra.
